{"tid":677361,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支那央視將有蟲虹鱒魚，硬說成「三文魚」","createTime":"2018-05-25T06:21:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-27T02:01:01.000Z","uid":29314,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"e51b8cf10043403429c98e2bef7cd0ce0b7d7ba6","tid":677361,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T06:21:05.000Z","msg":"說起三文魚，大部份人都會想到肥美的刺身。不過，近日央視財經竟將含有寄生蟲的養殖虹鱒魚，硬說成「三文魚」，還高調宣傳吹噓，結果引來網民狂轟。香港腸胃肝臟科專科醫生吳昊向《蘋果》指，淡水虹鱒魚體內或藏「中華肝吸蟲」，將淡水魚作刺身食用，有機會患上膽管癌。"},{"pid":"56ad095dc6ec2585b34d39c908d52c5606257f0d","tid":677361,"uid":29314,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T06:21:37.000Z","msg":"說起三文魚，大部份人都會想到肥美的刺身。不過，近日央視財經竟將含有寄生蟲的養殖虹鱒魚，硬說成「三文魚」，還高調宣傳吹噓，結果引來網民狂轟。香港腸胃肝臟科專科醫生吳昊向《蘋果》指，淡水虹鱒魚體內或藏「中華肝吸蟲」，將淡水魚作刺身食用，有機會患上膽管癌。<br />\n<br />\n繼續睇：<br />\n【亂食恐致癌】央視靠害！狂sell假三文魚養殖場掀怒火（&nbsp;<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2x8YKED￼&nbsp;）\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2x8YKED%EF%BF%BC%C2%A0%EF%BC%89&d=ZVrugfLkI%2B5%2F78SZCSYSSr%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=b721722c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2x8YKED￼&nbsp;）</a><br />\n【亂食死致癌】蔡瀾唔食三文魚刺身 「遲早食到成肚蟲，祝君好運」（&nbsp;<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2x4UmX8￼）\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2x4UmX8%EF%BF%BC%EF%BC%89&d=ZVrugfLkI%2B5%2F78SZCSYSSr%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=c71bc65a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2x4UmX8￼）</a><br />\n<br />\n央視財經日前播出節目《科技裏飄出的新「鮮」味》，指青海龍羊峽水庫有一個全國海拔最高，且最大的「三文魚」養殖場，強調「中國市場上三分之一的三文魚都被青藏高原『承包』了」。節目不斷吹噓養殖場的規模及先進技術，不過有網民卻踢爆，養殖場內所謂「三文魚」，其實是含有寄生蟲的淡水虹鱒魚。而養殖場的「三文魚」佔全國三分之一市場，港人北上，就隨時會吃下含寄生蟲的虹鱒魚而不自知，食用風險之大無法想像。"},{"pid":"bbf9b74996b38269fa1222db33a57213e36cd643","tid":677361,"uid":6222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T06:23:49.000Z","msg":"淡水魚生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9eccfa515f757b9b4605223b89995a7ae5c33662","tid":677361,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T06:24:55.000Z","msg":"中華肝吸蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"066448dab57b6cd7ab2b692dadcd650aed319975","tid":677361,"uid":63950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T06:29:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"733f6eec0fd7961473ba1f80e76446dd334eeade","tid":677361,"uid":79563,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T06:30:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s7.postimg.cc/t07zo7arv/image.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs7.postimg.cc%2Ft07zo7arv%2Fimage.jpg&h=47a35294&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"15f1cdc526b31b70e50ac7f01a893ff1419ddd62","tid":677361,"uid":92611,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bbf9b74996b38269fa1222db33a57213e36cd643","tid":677361,"uid":6222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T06:23:49.000Z","msg":"淡水魚生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T06:44:00.000Z","msg":"順德魚生"},{"pid":"68d0256a43e38c4624f50823b4e4a1f130a6a7d4","tid":677361,"uid":57410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T07:15:38.000Z","msg":"應該沒問題 佢比你食既三文魚都係呢隻架啦"},{"pid":"7364016ea89296e0319f5ab3940c36ad7fdfef01","tid":677361,"uid":135445,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"733f6eec0fd7961473ba1f80e76446dd334eeade","tid":677361,"uid":79563,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T06:30:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s7.postimg.cc/t07zo7arv/image.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs7.postimg.cc%2Ft07zo7arv%2Fimage.jpg&h=47a35294&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T07:18:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6af71a65d546a21fe45e5f9de42bf2264f96f90a","tid":677361,"uid":29314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T07:21:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>&lt;im